          <div class="hhs-rich-text c1">
            <p style="font-size: 36px; line-height: 1.5;"><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">Our Mission</span></p>
<p style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">To bring the best in class information and analysis together in one place. <a href="https://channel16.dryadglobal.com?hsLang=en" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Channel16 Maritime Risk Intelligence</a>&nbsp;is a free resource to help you and your organisation keep up to date on the world of Maritime Domain Intelligence.</span></p>
<hr>
<h2 style="font-size: 24px;">&nbsp;</h2>
<p style="font-size: 24px;"><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">From the Risk Intelligence Blog <em>'Channel 16' </em>Library: METIS Insights</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">Many more categories of knowledge and <a href="https://channel16.dryadglobal.com?hsLang=en" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Maritime Risk Intelligence on our Channel16 Knowledge HUb (coming soon!)</a></span></p>
            
          </div>
        </div>
